<div class="col-xs-12 horizontal-center">
  <div id="myModal" class="modal">

    <!-- Modal content -->
    <div class="modal-content">
      <!-- <span class="close">&times;</span> -->
      <p class="text-center" style="font-weight: bold;">thank you</p>
      <p class="text-center">HANG TIGHT! WEâ€™LL GET IN TOUCH WITH MORE DETAILS ON OUR LAUNCH. KNOW ANY OTHER BEAUTY BOSSES THAT MIGHT BENEFIT FROM BUILDING THEIR OWN SITE? REFER A FRIEND AND EARN CREDIT TOWARDS YOUR ACCOUNT.</p>
